article.title: Ethiopia's Import Exports in Q2 FY2022/23: Insights into Key Trading Partners
article.description: Ethiopia has established strong trade partnerships across continents, with significant contributions from Asia (36.8%), Europe (32.3%), Africa (19.2%), and the Americas (10.8%). This article explores the distribution of Ethiopia's exports to these regions, shedding light on the diverse trade dynamics that have propelled the country's export sector.
